## API Testing (PowerShell)

### Register
```powershell
$body = @{username="test";email="test@test.com";password="Test@123"} | ConvertTo-Json
Invoke-RestMethod -Uri "http://localhost:8950/api/auth/register" -Method POST -Body $body -ContentType "application/json"
```

### Login
```powershell
$body = @{username="test";password="Test@123"} | ConvertTo-Json
Invoke-RestMethod -Uri "http://localhost:8950/api/auth/login" -Method POST -Body $body -ContentType "application/json"
```

### AI Analysis (Protected)
```powershell
$token = "YOUR_JWT"
$body = @{chartData=@{};birthInfo=@{}} | ConvertTo-Json
Invoke-RestMethod -Uri "http://localhost:8950/api/ai/analyze" -Method POST -Body $body -ContentType "application/json" -Headers @{Authorization="Bearer $token"}
```

